        <div class='col icon-with-text-style-01 mb-50px sm-mb-40px'>
          <div class='feature-box feature-box-left-icon last-paragraph-no-margin'>
            <div class='feature-box-icon'>
              <i class='line-icon-Basket-Coins icon-extra-large text-base-color'></i>
            </div>
            <div class='feature-box-content'>
              <span class='d-inline-block alt-font text-dark-gray fw-600 mb-5px fs-20'
                >Meet your customer's requirements for LEED and BREEAM</span
              >
              <p class='w-90 md-w-100'>
                Around 70% of both global and European green building standards offer incentives or
                credits for using construction materials with EPDs.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- end features box item -->
        <!-- start features box item -->
        <div class='col icon-with-text-style-01 mb-50px sm-mb-40px'>
          <div class='feature-box feature-box-left-icon last-paragraph-no-margin'>
            <div class='feature-box-icon'>
              <i class='line-icon-Cursor-Click2 icon-extra-large text-base-color'></i>
            </div>
            <div class='feature-box-content'>
              <span class='d-inline-block alt-font text-dark-gray fw-600 mb-5px fs-20'
                >Optimize your carbon footprint</span
              >
              <p class='w-90 md-w-100'>
                Performing a life cycle assessment (LCA) allows you to gather a comprehensive
                inventory of all the components and substances employed in your product.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- end features box item -->
        <!-- start features box item -->
        <div class='col icon-with-text-style-01 mb-50px sm-mb-40px'>
          <div class='feature-box feature-box-left-icon last-paragraph-no-margin'>
            <div class='feature-box-icon'>
              <i class='line-icon-Bar-Chart2 icon-extra-large text-base-color'></i>
            </div>
            <div class='feature-box-content'>
              <span class='d-inline-block alt-font text-dark-gray fw-600 mb-5px fs-20'
                >Demonstrate your product's sustainability</span
              >
              <p class='w-90 md-w-100'>
                Acquiring an EPD for your product involves registering in environmental databases
                and life-cycle assessment (LCA) platforms.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- end features box item -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
